OOC: O.k. this has gone on long enough!  I'm sick and tired of this 
question simply being shrugged off (unless I missed the post in which 
case I apologize)!  Now if you people simply can't remember this 
let's review.  I left a while back.  I said that Cardhead could have 
Flicker, and Winged Warrior could have Owlhawk.  I came back.  
Cardhead told me she couldn't remember where Flicker was, but hadn't 
posted with him in a week so I could take over from whereever I 
wanted too.  Winged Warrior said roughly the same thing about 
Owlhawk, except he failed to mention whether or not he had even used 
Owlhawk, and for that matter if Owlhawk had finished his training 
with the Mech girl.  Now FOR PETE'S SAKE TELL ME!
